{"tid":1665371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好裝修期間用火魔法","createTime":"2019-10-20T14:24:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T14:28:58.000Z","uid":43696,"like":168,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"666c78a77349739a9864cabb19ff87cf3e9f8336","tid":1665371,"uid":43696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T14:24:07.000Z","msg":"裝修中資 黨企 係直搗黃龍既招數<br />\n一定要繼續做<br />\n<br />\n但真係唔好用火魔法<br />\n唔關好唔好睇 咩民意逆轉事<br />\n係安全問題<br />\n<br />\n好多呢d地鋪樓上 隔離左右都係民居<br />\n仲有好多係50-60年樓齡既唐樓黎<br />\n附近有餐廳燒中煤氣喉就仆得街<br />\n燒一燒遲早有一單大獲野<br />\n<br />\n繼續裝修+ 水魔法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打爆佢防火果d設施夠佢有排搞開唔到鋪"},{"pid":"25647d09440699bb9b6d60d0dd5a9013891b079f","tid":1665371,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T14:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c19bf29d4b18ed7b605b7a0ca5db7e4c768cd1b","tid":1665371,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T14:27:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48d69bc08fd958842b048d4124099926c3c2efb5","tid":1665371,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T14:30:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b4a4a028feeaf4a65faa91316e04e988e18234","tid":1665371,"uid":6043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T14:30:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80cf0edfde666ef7838ae8a7f899d4291789925f","tid":1665371,"uid":178368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T14:31:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"02dbaf33fc5096a454602719d4c7b92a92b9dc24","tid":1665371,"uid":46245,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T14:34:13.000Z","msg":"其實水魔法好過火魔法，一來形象上比火魔法好睇而有同樣破壞力，二來火魔法難控制好易殃及池魚，水魔法易控制得多"},{"pid":"800cd5aefe90af7df1076bbaec1788e0b81aae64","tid":1665371,"uid":41111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":